{"content": "<h2>The Artist: MintFace</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>MintFace is a Geodetic Reality Futurist who lays down a path for another person to one day pick up on. The image-laden pathway creates a legacy... and in doing so, becomes a way to understand the grit of the path less travelled, for those who choose it or it chooses them. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"997\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image01-4-769x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image01-4-769x1024.jpg 769w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image01-4-225x300.jpg 225w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image01-4-768x1023.jpg 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image01-4-1153x1536.jpg 1153w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image01-4-1537x2048.jpg 1537w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image01-4-400x533.jpg 400w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image01-4-1320x1759.jpg 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image01-4-600x799.jpg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image01-4.jpg 1874w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"What if you couldn't find your most precious person this Saturday?\n...and your last option is to leave digital clues.\nGeodetica is a trail of \"I'm over here\" messages for the disappeared to find.\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>MintFace</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t<h2>The Collection: Two Burdens</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Two Burdens is a study of the internal and external burdens we face. Acrylic on large panels worked over in layers and reduced back and built up again... like a sand bar for life. What remains at the end is the message. Two Burdens were minted in 2024 and owners eligible to acquire the physical framed 1/1 painting. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/5-Division-scaled.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"191700e\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\"5 Division\" data-e-action-hash=\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6NDQyNiwidXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6XC9cL3RoZWxpbmUud3RmXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8xMlwvNS1EaXZpc2lvbi1zY2FsZWQuanBnIiwic2xpZGVzaG93IjoiMTkxNzAwZSJ9\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2-Salvation-scaled.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"191700e\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\"2 Salvation\" data-e-action-hash=\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6NDQyNywidXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6XC9cL3RoZWxpbmUud3RmXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8xMlwvMi1TYWx2YXRpb24tc2NhbGVkLmpwZyIsInNsaWRlc2hvdyI6IjE5MTcwMGUifQ%3D%3D\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/8-Voyage-Ahead-scaled.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"191700e\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\"8 Voyage Ahead\" data-e-action-hash=\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6NDQyNCwidXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6XC9cL3RoZWxpbmUud3RmXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8xMlwvOC1Wb3lhZ2UtQWhlYWQtc2NhbGVkLmpwZyIsInNsaWRlc2hvdyI6IjE5MTcwMGUifQ%3D%3D\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\