ngs%3DeyJpZCI6NDQyMywidXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6XC9cL3RoZWxpbmUud3RmXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8xMlwvMS1CZXlvbmQtVGhlLU1lYWRvdy1zY2FsZWQuanBnIiwic2xpZGVzaG93IjoiMTkxNzAwZSJ9\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/22-Shanshui-山水-scaled.jpg\" data-elementor-open-lightbox=\"yes\" data-elementor-lightbox-slideshow=\"191700e\" data-elementor-lightbox-title=\"22 Shanshui (山水)\" data-e-action-hash=\"#elementor-action%3Aaction%3Dlightbox%26settings%3DeyJpZCI6NDQyMiwidXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6XC9cL3RoZWxpbmUud3RmXC93cC1jb250ZW50XC91cGxvYWRzXC8yMDI0XC8xMlwvMjItU2hhbnNodWktXHU1YzcxXHU2YzM0LXNjYWxlZC5qcGciLCJzbGlkZXNob3ciOiIxOTE3MDBlIn0%3D\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t<h2>A Specific Artwork: Fallout</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>'Fallout' puts the viewer in the immediate aftermath of catastrophe. A form in the top left is unravelling, perhaps following the demise of the charcoal colored form centre mass. A vibrant scene characterised by bruised skin tones in a waterside location. Available in The Line Gift Shop for 0.20 eth.</p><p>Available in The Line Gift Shop for 0.20 eth. <a href=\"https://giftshop.theline.wtf/token/ETHEREUM:0xe1d1f99505a13d20b25d5ef32280771d7eb5ed09:6\">Shop Now</a></p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://giftshop.theline.wtf/token/ETHEREUM:0xe1d1f99505a13d20b25d5ef32280771d7eb5ed09:6\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"1000\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fallout-767x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fallout-767x1024.jpg 767w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fallout-225x300.jpg 225w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fallout-768x1025.jpg 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fallout-1151x1536.jpg 1151w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fallout-1535x2048.jpg 1535w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fallout-400x533.jpg 400w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fallout-1320x1761.jpg 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fallout-600x801.jpg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Fallout-scaled.jpg 1919w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://oncyber.io/line910\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tMintFace | Line 910\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t<p>Two Burdens collection launched in 2024 and caps of a decade off creative projects that MintFace has pursued to document for legacy. View the proof of work at <a href=\"https://geodeti.ca/\">geodeti.ca</a></p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"421\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image02-4-1024x575.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image02-4-1024x575.jpg 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image02-4-300x169.jpg 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image02-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image02-4-1536x863.jpg 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image02-4-2048x1151.jpg 2048w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image02-4-800x450.jpg 800w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image02-4-1320x742.jpg 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/image02-4-600x337.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />"}